In computer science~\cite{myref}...
\chapter{...}
...
\printbibliography
\end{document}
\end{lstlisting}
This example sets a \File{hpitr} report that
 \begin{itemize}
 \item is an original report (\lstinline|trtype=singlereport|),
 \item uses Biblatex with \hologo{biber},
